{"tha-ap477:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap477:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap477:0.3":"Kummasadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap477:1.1":"“Esanaya carantassa, ","tha-ap477:1.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap477:1.3":"Rittakam pattam disvana, ","tha-ap477:1.4":"kummasam purayim aham. ","tha-ap477:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap477:2.2":"yam bhikkham adadim tada; ","tha-ap477:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap477:2.4":"kummasassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap477:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap477:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap477:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap477:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap477:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap477:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap477:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap477:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap477:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap477:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kummasadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap477:7.1":"Kummasadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}